Text: FWMessage From Missy Herndon mailto Sent Friday February AM To Herndon Wayne Subject RE Hey about this stock It is a share now Next week it will jump to but if you talk to him today you will lock into todays price In days from Feb it going public or planning to to a share If the company folds you are guaranteed per share If they sell the company you are guaranteed share He will give you a certificate that at anytime you can get yur money back Owner was offered million to sell he is waiting for it to go million The guys name is Greg Hodge and his phone number is x Mom is a friend of his mother Kay and Janie Original Message From Herndon Wayne mailto Sent Thursday February PM To Subject hey cutie whats going on you having a good day so far i miss you and look forward to seeing you tonite Luv Ya Cute
